---
title: Spiced Mushrooms, Beyond Meat® and Lentil Dal with Garlic-Cilantro Naan and Yogurt Sauce
description: Tonight's veggie dinner is as comforting as it is delicious. Earthy, spiced lentils are stewed and serve as the perfect base for Beyond Meat®, meaty mushrooms and bright pops of tomato. Buttery, toasted naan is served alongside to mop up all the flavourful goodness!
